metadata.name: GLITCH
metadata.description:
Underneath the word I live in there’s a place where anxiety and disappointment built a castle and live in chaos , you can feel but you can’t see.

Constantly hear the voices inside of your head you turn around and it’s just nothing there.
Don’t worry it’s just a glitch of humankind.
Start myself in the mirror for just one second I can see freaks through my eye hand to hand dancing.
Welcome to my brain.
I can feel my hands getting wet and burning , mirror is not there anymore.
Mirror mirror on the wall tell no more lies of who we are.
